headline.main: FIJIS NEW PACIFIC LINK; United States Bases There Are on Main Sea Routes

lead_paragraph: Establishment of American bases in the Fiji Islands is a matter of national interest, says a bulletin of the National Geographic Society.
abstract: Natl Geographic Soc bulletin cites importance of US Fiji Islands bases
